<h2>Service Worker on Rails</h2>

<p>
  <%= image_tag 'turtle-logo-120x120.png', style: 'float:right' %>
  The Service Worker Rails Sandbox is a collection of examples using Service Workers on Rails. The sandbox makes use of the
  <%= link_to "#" do %>
    <code>serviceworker-rails</code>
  <% end %>
  gem which makes it easier to integrate Service Worker scripts with the Rails asset pipeline. You can find the <%= link_to "source code of the sandbox", "#" %> and the
  <%= link_to "#" do %>
    <code>serviceworker-rails</code>
  <% end %>
  gem on GitHub.
</p>

<% demo_index.each do |section, pages| %>
  <h4><%= section %></h4>
  <ul>
    <% pages.each do |title, path| %>
      <li>
        <%= link_to title, page_path(path) %>
      </li>
    <% end %>
  </ul>
<% end %>

<p>
  On your mobile device, try adding the sandbox to your homescreen. The turtle icon is by Carla Dias from the Noun Project.
</p>

